headline: European Infection Control Market Forecast Report 2025-2030: Outsourcing Trends Among Pharma & Medical Device Firms Boost Europe's Infection Control Market Growth
summary: Key market growth drivers include the rise in surgeries, advancements in sterilization technology, and increased outsourcing among healthcare providers. Germany is expected to lead the market due to robust health spending and technological adoption. Cleaning and disinfection products are projected to hold the largest market share, while hospitals and clinics remain the primary end-users.
